caption.p: Effects of rFIP-mco on inflammatory cytokines in LPS treated THP-1 cells. Cells were stimulated with LPS (1 μg/ml) for 24 h, and then were treated with gradient concentration of rFIP-mco for 24 h. (A) Cell viability of the THP-1 cells were determined. (B) TNF-α, (C) IL-1β, and (D) IL-6 releases were analyzed by ELISA. * P < 0.05 vs. control groups (untreated cells).
